{"tid":1883391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日增六患者 擬改防疫對策","createTime":"2020-02-17T02:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T02:34:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a80b37d8a4d751de0a5f22b9b2638ee217cc876e","tid":1883391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/PKF4CBYQPCKSL3RBS7HO5SGAAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FPKF4CBYQPCKSL3RBS7HO5SGAAY%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5ce967f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FPKF4CBYQPCKSL3RBS7HO5SGAAY%2F&h=8e2b3225\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/PKF4CBYQPCKSL3RBS7HO5SGAAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n日增六患者 擬改防疫對策<br />\n<br />\n日本新型冠狀病毒疫繼續擴大，昨日再有六人確診，當中東京五人、愛知縣一人。厚生勞動省擬改變防疫對策，從加強邊境防疫轉為重點放在「早期發現與治療」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：任職跨國建築師樓  全體員工留家一周<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200217/large/1581871042_bafa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200217%2Flarge%2F1581871042_bafa.jpg&h=c02731a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在甘肅省保健院，護士為方便穿除防護服集體剃髮。新華社<br />\n<br />\n改為着重「早期發現與治療」<br />\n<br />\n東京都政府宣佈，昨日新增確診的五名男子，年齡介乎30至60多歲，其中三人與1月18日屋形船上舉行的士工公會新年聚餐參與者有接觸：一名60多歲的司機、一名的士司機的30多歲家人，以及跟聚餐中另一確診者有接觸的一名60多歲醫護人員。該飯局至今已有至少13宗個案。另兩名確診者，包括一名30多歲男性辦公室文員及一名60多歲住在埼玉縣的司機。他們都沒有外遊、沒有接觸屋形船聚會參與者。但該辦公室文員有同事確診。<br />\n<br />\n另外，愛知縣一名60多歲男子確診，他曾跟名古屋一名60多歲女患者接觸。該女患者跟丈夫早前到美國夏威夷旅遊行後回國確診。<br />\n<br />\n目前日本有的確診個案分佈在全國11個縣府，不少都無法掌握傳染途徑，厚生勞動大臣加藤勝信指，政府擬改變防疫對策，從加強邊境防疫轉為重點放在「早期發現與治療」，包括要求所有地方政府設置「回國者、接觸者電話諮詢中心」。撇除「鑽石公主號」郵輪個案，日本國內已有59宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n除了日本，新加坡疫情亦持續擴大，昨日再新增三宗確診，兩宗跟早有多人染病的基督教神召會恩典堂有關；一宗就跟另一名確診個案有關。<span style=\"color: orange;\">而南韓<span style=\"color: gold;\">時隔六日後</span>，昨日再出現一宗新增個案，患者之前沒有出國。</span><br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》/日本放送協會/中央社"},{"pid":"6db4e491700ee53f09423c3d21f65485fef2d433","tid":1883391,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好做唔做"},{"pid":"794884b64de8829041e1993d4d707170cc015e01","tid":1883391,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"封關啦"},{"pid":"b432c40b67c5f1bd1a22f5ae540b75fb231c048e","tid":1883391,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"要剃頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d48997645fab1ddf06bdc04f5e04f5afb88722","tid":1883391,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b432c40b67c5f1bd1a22f5ae540b75fb231c048e","tid":1883391,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"要剃頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:25:00.000Z","msg":"甘肅省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91f7ef75357b98edbd2d5f93be409d1b538fc17","tid":1883391,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好封關咁無骨氣呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771da2435e439437209ec440317d00046dd89f1a","tid":1883391,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n都無大流行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047209c9bbe3eb397ee9ebe1bcac02709f7a7556","tid":1883391,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a80b37d8a4d751de0a5f22b9b2638ee217cc876e","tid"